articles.author: William Earl
articles.title: International Emmy Awards: Martin Freeman, Amazon’s ‘La Caída,’ Netflix’s ‘The Empress’ Among Top Winners - Variety
articles.description: Martin Freeman, Netflix's 'The Empress' and Amazon's 'La Caída' were among the top winners Monday at the 51st annual International Emmy Awards.
articles.content: Turkish telenovela “Yargi,” German miniseries “The Empress,” Mexican drama “La Caída” and actor Martin Freeman were among the top winners at the 51st annual International Emmy Awards, held Monday at … [+6624 chars]
